title: Day 1289
content:
# Day 1289

I must say getting outside and socializing is so nice. It makes me think I need to sign my kid up for sports.

![I am the golden tee champion](https://miro.medium.com/1*fYA2WIro3-prllKYAqI_Qg.png)

![Trivia champions](https://miro.medium.com/1*5P3EwbSNIuUglZNtCayoHA.png)

It's good to get outside. On the one hand I am grateful for my work from home job, but humans were meant to socialize. So when I get the chance it's a real treat to get outside and socialize with my buddies.

10/1/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
